<section class="fact-box" id="fun-facts">
    <h2>Fun Facts About Exoplanets</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>There are over 5,000 confirmed exoplanets in our galaxy!</li>
        <li>Some exoplanets are made entirely of diamond.</li>
        <li>Exoplanets can be hotter than stars!</li>
        <li>Some exoplanets have two suns, like Tatooine in Star Wars!</li>
        <li>Some exoplanets orbit neutron stars, leading to extreme gravitational forces!</li>
    </ul>
</section>

